name: Kohe 5
description: Hell is starting to break open in in front of your eyes. You are in a small Maes of death and you will get some Bloodshedder done to you by all the Kakoka Balls. Kunun is also in jail outside and you must destroy the myth bug in order to find the solution. The solution to prevent further overheating to the past eras of Kohe! So anyway I must warn you that Love can hurt, so be even more careful and enjoy the mission!
